#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module provides an interface to view and select splash screen themes."
msgstr ""
"Modul ini menyediakan sebuah antarmuka untuk menampilkan dan memilih tema-"
"tema layar splash."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the splash screen manager"
msgstr "Ini adalah sebuah screenshot-nya pengelola layar splash"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "The splash screen manager module"
msgstr "Modul pengelola layar splash"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can see previews of already installed splash screens. The "
"preview of the current splash screen is highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Pada halaman ini kamu bisa melihat pratinjau dari layar splash yang sudah "
"terinstal. Pratinjau dari layar splash saat ini yang telah tersorot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Hover a preview image with the mouse cursor then the button "
#| "<guilabel>Test Splashscreen</guilabel> appears at the bottom right of the "
#| "image. Press this button to view the splashscreen in action."
msgid ""
"Hover a preview image with the mouse cursor then the button "
"<guilabel>Preview Splash Screen</guilabel> appears at the bottom right of "
"the image. Press this button to view the splashscreen in action."
msgstr ""
"Melayangi sebuah citra pratinjau dengan kursor mouse kemudian tekan "
"<guilabel>Uji Splashscreen</guilabel> yang muncul di sebelah kanan bawah "
"citra. Tekanlah tombol ini untuk menampilkan aksinya splashscreen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Splash Screen"
msgid "Get New Splash Screens..."
msgstr "Layar Splash"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to be connected to the Internet to use this action. A dialog will "
"display a list of themes from the <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org"
"\">https://store.kde.org</ulink> website. Clicking the <guibutton>Install</"
"guibutton> button associated with a theme will install this theme locally."
msgstr ""
"Anda perlu Internet yang terkoneksi untuk menggunakan aksi ini. Sebuah "
"dialog akan mendisplaikan daftar tema dari situs <ulink url=\"https://store."
"kde.org\">https://store.kde.org</ulink>. Mengeklik tombol <guibutton>Instal</"
"guibutton> yang terkait dengan tema akan menginstal tema ini secara lokal."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Installing a new theme</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Menginstal sebuah tema baru</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Installing a new theme</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Menginstal sebuah tema baru</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This new theme is immediately available after you close the "
#| "&systemsettings; Add-On Installer dialog and is highlighted. The preview "
#| "displays the picture. You need to click the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> "
#| "button to make this theme your current splash-screen theme."
msgid ""
"This new theme is immediately available after you close the &systemsettings; "
"Download New Splash Screens dialog and is highlighted. The preview displays "
"the picture. You need to click the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button to "
"make this theme your current splash-screen theme."
msgstr ""
"Tema baru ini tersedia segera setelah kamu menutup dialog Penginstal Pernik "
"&systemsettings; dan tersorot. Pratinjau mendisplaikan gambar. Kamu perlu "
"mengeklik tombol <guibutton>Terapkan</guibutton> untuk membuat tema ini "
"menjadi tema layar splash-mu saat ini."

